==================================================
CHANGE — Mockery v3 + testify test setup
Date: 2026-03-30
==================================================

==================================================
GOAL
==================================================

Every interface in `internal/port` should have generated mocks, and the
application-layer tests should use generated mocks plus testify assertions.

==================================================
WHAT CHANGED
==================================================

1. MOCK GENERATION

  Added:
    .mockery.yml
    tools/tools.go

  Uses:
    - mockery v3
    - testify template output

  Generated mocks for all current ports under:
    internal/port/mocks/

2. TEST STACK

  Added/testify usage in:
    internal/application/api_test.go

  Replaced hand-written fakes with generated mockery mocks for:
    - ProblemRepository
    - SubmissionRepository
    - SessionRepository
    - ReviewRepository
    - RegistryRepository
    - EvaluationPublisher

3. DEPENDENCIES

  Added:
    github.com/stretchr/testify
    github.com/vektra/mockery/v3

==================================================
CURRENT STATE
==================================================

- app-layer tests now use generated mocks, not manual fakes
- all interfaces in internal/port have generated mocks
- mock generation is standardized through mockery v3 config
- hexagonal ports now have a repeatable testing story

==================================================
VERIFICATION
==================================================

- go test ./internal/application/...  → passes
- go build ./...              → passes
